      "colorKeywords":  "Optional. Array of { word, color } objects to highlight key terms in the description.",
      "answerType":          "'select-node' | 'select-nodes' | 'multiple-choice'. select-node = single double-click; select-nodes = multi-double-click (requires requiredSelections); multiple-choice = radio buttons.",
